"7016A049100a V-1.00" appears to be silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :There appears to be an ''[[IDT]]'' PCI-Express switch on the board (89HPES5T5 ?). :A2HP02 is printed on the label of one of the wireless modules.
The device appears to be identical to the [[EnGenius EIR900]]. :The device is manufactured by [[Senao]].
All of the antennas used are ''Airgain'' antennas (3x N2420DS, 3x N5x20SC).
===PSU=== The power adapter included with the unit is a '''Powertron Electronics''' :PA1045-120HUB (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 1.0A -> 12VDC, 3.3A)
